GCMC CO2 in IRMOF

use gaspressure
finish

temperature 208.0 # temp in K

ewald prec 1e-6

steps         10000000
equilibration 1000000
print         100000
stack         10000
sample coordinates 100000

# GCMC optimisation
acceptmolmoveupdate 10000
acceptmolmoveratio 0.5
acceptmolrotupdate 10000
acceptmolrotratio  0.5

# GCMC moves
move molecule    1 25
CO2
move rotatemol   1 25
CO2
move gcinsertmol 1 50 1.0  # atom types, freq, overlap distance
CO2 {pressure}

start
